<h1>Birmingham International Airport</h1>
<p>BHX Birmingham Airport is an unofficial guide to help you get the most from your visit to the airport.  You will find details for flight information, airport hotels, route maps and more.</p>				
<div id="main_list">
<div class="main_list_item" id="latest-news"><h3>Latest News</h3><div class="leftpic"><img src="Dev/images/birmingham_departure_board.jpg" alt="Birmingham Airport Departure Board" /></div><p>Royal Assent has been given on the construction of HS2.</p><p><a href="/hs2.php">View Story</a></p></div><div class="main_list_item" id="flight_times"><h3>Live Arrival and Departure Boards</h3><div class="leftpic"><img src="Dev/images/birmingham_departure_board.jpg" alt="Birmingham Airport Departure Board" /></div><p>Flights can often get delayed, or even cancelled in unfortunate circumstances, so why not check our live departure and arrivals data to ensure you have the latest info.</p><p><a href="/arrivals_departures.php">View Arrivals &amp; Departures</a></p></div>
<div class="main_list_item" id="hotels"><h3>Hotels</h3>    <div class="leftpic"><img src="Dev/images/novotel_birmingham_airport.jpg" alt="novotel birmingham airport" /></div> <p>There are a number of hotels to choose from that are suitable for flying from Birmingham Airport, including on-site hotels such the <a href="/novotel.php">Novotel</a> and <a href="/ibis.php">Ibis</a>, and off-site hotels such as the <a href="/hilton-birmingham-metropole.php">Hilton</a> and <a href="/holiday-inn.php">Holiday Inn</a>.</p><p><a href="/hotels.php">Birmingham Airport Hotels</a></p></div><div class="main_list_item" id="parking"><h3>Parking</h3><div class="leftpic"><img src="Dev/images/birmingham_airport_parking.jpg" alt="birmingham airport parking" /></div><p>If you need car parking at Birmingham Airport there are a number of options, and choosing the most suitable one will ensure that you don't spend more than you need to. Choose form the quick 'Drop &amp; Go' or Short and Long Term options.</p><p><a href="/parking.php">Birmingham Airport Parking</a></p></div><div class="main_list_item" id="destinations"><h3>News</h3><div class="leftpic"><img src="Dev/images/birmingham_destinations.jpg" alt="news from birmingham airport" /></div><p>Stay up to date with stories about Birmingham Airport.</p><p><a href="/news.php">News from Birmingham Airport</a></p></div>
